-announcement-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/SharonVanEtten-new-single-Afterlife-announcement-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/SharonVanEtten-new-single-Afterlife-announcement-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/SharonVanEtten-new-single-Afterlife-announcement-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/SharonVanEtten-new-single-Afterlife-announcement-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sharon-van-etten">莎朗·范·埃滕 (Sharon Van Etten)</a>宣布推出一首名为“Afterlife”的新单曲 - 请查看下面的预告片片段。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/sharon-van-etten-cover-interview-2022-weve-been-going-about-this-all-wrong-3204585">Sharon Van Etten：“我必须充满希望。我是一名母亲，我想为了我的儿子勇敢”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位新泽西歌手兼词曲作家上周开始在社交媒体上分享一系列帖子，以此表明她的回归。她发布了两​​张由脉冲合成线配乐的黑白图像。</p><p>随后，Van Etten 上传了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sharon-van-etten-reveals-venue-for-secret-london-show-heres-how-to-buy-tickets-3774094">她今年夏天在伦敦 100 Club 举行的亲密表演</a>的片段。 “即将推出，”她在标题中写道。</p><p>这位音乐家现在在网上发布了另一个新材料的预览片段，确认了一首名为“Afterlife”的曲目。预计将于下周三（10 月 23 日）发布 -<a href="https://sharon-van-etten.lnk.to/afterlife" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处预保存/预添加</a>。</p><p>这首即将发行的歌曲被称为 Sharon Van Etten &amp; The Attachment Theory——这是她在最近的演出中使用的绰号。今年七月，它在伦敦进行了现场首演。查看下面的帖子。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DBHph-5RVjX/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; 