rifier-3-Signature-Entertainment.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/David-Howard-Thornton-as-Art-the-Clown-in-Terrifier-3-Signature-Entertainment-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/David-Howard-Thornton-as-Art-the-Clown-in-Terrifier-3-Signature-Entertainment-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/David-Howard-Thornton-as-Art-the-Clown-in-Terrifier-3-Signature-Entertainment-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/David-Howard-Thornton-as-Art-the-Clown-in-Terrifier-3-Signature-Entertainment-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/David-Howard-Thornton-as-Art-the-Clown-in-Terrifier-3-Signature-Entertainment-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3795696" class="wp-caption-text">大卫·霍华德·桑顿在《恐怖片》中饰演小丑阿特。图片来源：Signature Entertainment</figcaption></figure><p>至于该系列将如何结束，导演对一件事充满信心：“目前，我可以肯定地说，我知道它如何结束，而且这将是史诗般的。” <a href="https://screenrant.com/terrifier-4-movie-david-howard-thornton-update/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">莱昂内在《恐怖分子 3》上映之前就确认了第四部电影的拍摄，尽管在宣布消息时他还没有写好剧本</a>。</p><p>低成本邪教恐怖片系列的第三部也是最新作品已于周五（10 月 11 日）上映。这部以圣诞节为背景的电影讲述了连环杀人案小丑阿特（Art The Clown）追逐西耶娜·肖（劳伦·拉维拉饰）的故事，她试图在上一部电影的事件发生后重建自己的生活。</p><p>原版<i>《恐怖片》</i>于 2018 年上映。这部由莱昂内编剧和导演的电影，预算仅为 35,000 美元，讲述了神秘小丑的故事，凭借其高血腥程度在社交媒体上掀起了一场风暴，并为<i>《恐怖片 2》</i>赢得了足够的票房呈绿灯亮起。 </p><figure id="attachment_3795695" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3795695" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3795695" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/David-Howard-Thornton-as-Art-the-Clown-in-Terrifier-3-Signature-Entertainment-2.jpg" alt="大卫·霍华德·桑顿在恐怖片中饰演小丑阿特" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/David-Howard-Thornton-as-Art-the-Clown-in-Terrifier-3-Signature-Entertainment-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/David-Howard-Thornton-as-Art-the-Clown-in-Terrifier-3-Signature-Entertainment-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/David-Howard-Thornton-as-Art-the-Clown-in-Terrifier-3-Signature-Entertainment-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/David-Howard-Thornton-as-Art-the-Clown-in-Terrifier-3-Signature-Entertainment-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/David-Howard-Thornton-as-Art-the-Clown-in-Terrifier-3-Signature-Entertainment-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/David-Howard-Thornton-as-Art-the-Clown-in-Terrifier-3-Signature-Entertainment-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3795695" class="wp-caption-text">大卫·霍华德·桑顿在《恐怖片》中饰演小丑阿特。图片来源：Signature Entertainment</figcaption></figure><p>这部续集（再次由莱昂内执导）以这一声誉为基础，制作成本约为 25 万美元，据报道<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/killer-clown-horror-terrifier-2-is-causing-people-to-pass-out-in-cinemas-3328142">导致人们在电影院昏倒</a>，全球票房收入超过 1,500 万美元。后来，在由恐怖专业刊物<i>《血腥恶心》</i>发起的 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/terrifier-2-oscars-troll-academy-nominated-horror-3342084">粉丝驱动的活动中，该片被提交奥斯卡考虑</a>，但最终空手而归。</p><p>去年，编剧兼导演达米安·莱昂内 (Damien Leone) 和法国发行商 The Coven 的总裁兼创始人普里西拉·史密斯 (Priscilla Smith) 透露， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/terrifier-3-release-date-cast-plot-extreme-violence-budget-3450694">该系列的第三部作品将比前几部更加血腥，并且预算也会大幅增加</a>。</p><p>后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/terrifier-franchise-could-end-with-fourth-movie-teases-director-3802764">《恐怖分子》系列可能会以第四部电影结束，戏弄导演</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
